==Chiricahua==

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|[nòn]}}

===Etymology===

Cognates: Navajo ''[[nooʼ]]'', Western Apache ''[[non]]~[[noi]]'', Mescalero ''[[nun]]'', Plains Apache ''[[nǫǫ]]''.

===Noun===
'''non'''

# [[grave]], [[burial]] place, [[cache]]

===Alternate spelling===

The spelling ''non'' is used in older Americanist literature.

